{"tid":1312434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水衝突　警：示威者用鐵枝、粉末襲警　多名警員受傷　追究到底","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T08:54:16.000Z","uid":68738,"like":9,"dislike":530,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"f62b45ec6b796cbfe5f088bffe8ad5d689995535","tid":1312434,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/POLICE-wound-0713_DWIOm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FPOLICE-wound-0713_DWIOm_1200x0.png&h=8b456d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n針對水貨客問題的「光復上水」遊行，今天下午約五時結束後，大量示威者隨即與警察在街頭爆發衝突，警方出動胡椒噴劑及警棍驅趕，示威則向警察投擲雨傘、水橂等物品。警方晚上九時許在社交媒體發佈警員受傷照片，指在今日上水遊行後的非法集結事件中，有多批暴力示威者蓄意使用鐵枝、疑似刺激性粉末等不同的武器及物品襲擊警察，導致多名警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱強烈譴責暴力示威者的刻意襲擊行為，並強調會對所有非法及暴力行為進行調查，追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%94%A8%E9%90%B5%E6%9E%9D-%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AB%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95/?fbclid=IwAR3salThrUp2_SADK-COLzrBCP7VC2-f34hPT4-aEOO_IeCgqsvmiOxLThw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259E%259D-%25E7%25B2%2589%25E6%259C%25AB%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3salThrUp2_SADK-COLzrBCP7VC2-f34hPT4-aEOO_IeCgqsvmiOxLThw&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRKz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=8db44af1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%2